      "originalText": "Total ranges =\n\n5.62\n×\n10\n14\n1.2\n×\n10\n9\n1.2×10\n9\n5.62×10\n14\n        ​\n\n\n≈ 4.5 × 10⁵ ≈ 500,000 ranges",
