      "originalText": "How are we are taking care of randomnes \n- we are picking one ticket server at random\n- From the ticket server we are picking one\n  range at random.\n- From that range we are picking currentValue\n  we are doing ++ in TRANSACTION like above.\n- that integer comes to API and then encoded \n   and stored as short_code i the URL DB",
